<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.6">
<l>poṅku nīṇmuṭi yamararkaḷ toḻuteḻa vamutiṉaik koṭuttaḷippāṉ</l>
<l>aṅko rāmaiya tākiya vātiniṉ ṉaṭimaiyai yaruḷeṉakku</l>
<l>taṅku pēṭaiyo ṭūṭiya matukaran taiyalār kuḻalaṇaivāṉ</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷ tōyceṉṉi māṭañceṉ ṟaṇaitiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Primal [Lord] who became a tortoise that day to bestow nectar,</l>
<l rend="indent">having brought [it] forth,</l>
<l>As immortals with bright, high crowns appeared worshipping,</l>
<l rend="indent">[graciously] grant me devotion to you,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where a honeybee,</l>
<l rend="indent">which quarreled with its mate who stayed [behind],</l>
<l>Approaches a mansion with a [roof]top that touches the moon,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming to cling in a lady’s curls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
